# ANAGRAMS

ğŸ”´ğŸŸ¡ğŸŸ¢Two strings are anagrams if:
   1.They contain exactly the same characters
   2.Each character occurs the same number of times
   3.The order of characters does not matter

String 1	       String 2	  Are they anagrams?
listen	      silent	         âœ… Yes
triangle       integral          âœ… Yes
